fulltitle: Michael Parenti: Marxism & the Crisis in Eastern Europe (1990)
title: Michael Parenti: Marxism & the Crisis in Eastern Europe (1990)
_filename: _Michael Parenti - Marxism & the Crisis in Eastern Europe (1990).webm
description:
http://alternativeradio.org | Michael Parenti is a brilliant orator and one of this country's foremost independent political analysts. He has taught at major colleges and universities in the U.S. and abroad. He is the author of numerous books including 'Democracy for the Few', 'The Face of Imperialism' and 'The Assassination of Julius Caesar'.

Recorded in Northridge, CA on April 04, 1990.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
